v1.4.2 2019.01.25
- PONRTSYS-3007: pontop uses ~25MBytes memory for buffering
  + Make TOP maximum line length and maximum line number configurable

v1.4.1 2017.03.03
- GPONSW-3180: otop -b generates gtop.txt (with otop content) instead of otop.txt
  + Function top_batch expanded by adding file_name parameter

v1.4.0 2016.07.07
- Update License to BSD/GPLv2
