v1.2.1 - 2014.01.23

- GPONSW-1694: 'otop' too small with Ethernet connection (D2 board, eCos)
  + use default top 120x38 window
  + clear footer line

v1.2.0 - 2014.01.09
- GPONSW-1648: eCos: gtop -b terminates abnormally
  + eCos line length increased from 100 to 128 chars

